    <!-- ============================================================ -->
    <!-- CATERING SET: Grand Opening                                  -->
    <!-- ============================================================ -->

    <record id="set_grand_opening" model="lcs.catering.set">
        <field name="name">Grand Opening Package 開張盛事到會套餐</field>
        <field name="product_id" ref="product_grand_opening"/>
        <field name="recommendation">All-inclusive Grand Opening Package — HK$16,388 fixed.

WORKFLOW:
1. Pick the Package Fee line first (HK$16,388 — the bundle).
2. Pick ONE Suckling Pig variant (Spanish OR Chinese — included).
3. The ceremonial items (Lo Hei, Prosecco, drinks) come pre-included at qty 0 surcharge.
4. Pick exactly 4 canapes (40 pcs each = 160 pcs total).
   • Mini Rainbow Angus Beef Burger adds +HK$250 per 40 pcs.
5. Add optional upgrades (Champagne / Dummy Cake / Golden Pig) as needed.

INCLUDED:
• 1 Suckling Pig (3-4kg) with on-site chef carving
• 1 tray Prosperity Toss (Lo Hei) - Smoked Salmon
• 2 bottles Sparkling Wine (Prosecco DOC) + 12 Champagne Glasses
• Orange juice, soft drinks, mineral water (~100 cups)
• Decor: 2 red tablecloths, 6 gold scissors, opening ribbon ball
• 2 waiters / 4 hours (1hr setup + 2hr service + 1hr dismantle)
• 50 reusable tableware sets, food trays, heat lamps, tongs, labels
• Ice bucket, punch bowl, ice, glassware
• Round-trip delivery (door-to-door)

NOTE: Set is sized for ~50 guests; quantities on each line are FIXED (do not enter guest count expecting per-person scaling).</field>
    </record>

